thread.title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Changjiang Electronics Technology sees FY 2017 net profit up 220 pct to 258 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Jiangsu Changjiang Electronics Technology sees FY 2017 net profit up 220 pct to 258 pct

organizations.name: jiangsu changjiang electronics technology co ltd

text:
Jan 23(Reuters) - Jiangsu Changjiang Electronics Technology Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 220 percent to 258 percent, or to increase by 234 million yuan to 274 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 106.3 million yuan
* The reason for the forecast is effect from main business performance and subsidiary stake change Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/JV7aoE Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
